{"tid":1418422,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本社運失敗的歷史","createTime":"2019-08-05T18:40:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T14:53:43.000Z","uid":84944,"like":75,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"d8975fb37018c722414a757d935588c6a4429020","tid":1418422,"uid":84944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:40:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/international/日本社運失敗的歷史/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E7%A4%BE%E9%81%8B%E5%A4%B1%E6%95%97%E7%9A%84%E6%AD%B7%E5%8F%B2%2F&d=bDHmYwogulq9FkNLxWxOtqzbj60slk4H2lWqI%2F1XlBQ%3D&h=0601a58e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E7%A4%BE%E9%81%8B%E5%A4%B1%E6%95%97%E7%9A%84%E6%AD%B7%E5%8F%B2%2F&h=15879f3e\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/international/日本社運失敗的歷史/</a><br />\n<br />\n兩個重點：<br />\n<strong>1. 不可分化</strong><br />\n（eg. 勇武和理非互鬧，意見不合就話三毛p牌）連連登同溫層都分化，出面仲點有人支持？<br />\n<br />\n<strong>2. 保民意</strong><br />\n要知外面絕大部分黃係淺黃，儘量避免傷及無辜（例如燒宿舍）、塞地鐵等大失民心既行為，保住得來不易的光環，政府家下就係想我地失民意不攻自破<br />\n<br />\n希望連登仲容得下和理非意見"},{"pid":"248d2ea7a4e043e0bcd5bf0f4beb46bbcfff8686","tid":1418422,"uid":65354,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:42:26.000Z","msg":"二百萬人當中 極多係和理非<br />\n佢地好多唔鍾意見到暴力場面 今日亦唔敢罷工<br />\n<br />\n我地唯有用和理非手段 拉攏返佢地<br />\n叫佢地參與罷買 同機場集會<br />\n<br />\n兩個行動都係安全同低風險 效果亦大<br />\n最緊要係可以增加返佢地參與度 唔好俾佢地變得麻木 唔好同我地割萬4"},{"pid":"d4b41458e3d8e50aa06c38bf68661b6e0c43a2a8","tid":1418422,"uid":235174,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:42:38.000Z","msg":"當年X教授同磁力王既爭拗又再響呢度重新出現，都係講d咁既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2ea8403b5bc3c72e88a5435342219aba78ed134","tid":1418422,"uid":76216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:43:14.000Z","msg":"建議］ p牌正負評顯示<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https: